I’m not sure if there is something similar to “module_instance” but I have done something like this before:

in your base.html:
```{% set faq_instances = {val : 0} %}
{% block body %}
{% endblock body %}```

then in your module
```{% if !faq_instances.val %}
DO SCHEMA
{% endif %}
{% do faq_instances.update({val : 1}) %}```
